The way products look on our sim rig is pretty important to most of us. We may claim that it's not, but when there are very few prizes for us to win in sim racing, we tend to just buy our own. These Cube Controls pedals are the ultimate trophy to reward yourself for your hard work and dedication to sim racing. But are they all show and no go? Let's find out. I'm Laurence, welcome to the channel.

